snippet: Japan's Kei Nishikori maintained his impressive clay-court form to outclass Russian Andrey Kuznetsov 6-3 6-3 6-3 in the second round of the French Open on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Japan's Kei Nishikori maintained his impressive clay-court form to outclass Russian Andrey Kuznetsov 6-3 6-3 6-3 in the second round of the French Open on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Impressive Nishikori Races Into Third Round in Paris
headline.main: Impressive Nishikori Races Into Third Round in Paris
